<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Gurpreet Kaur | Portfolio</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

body {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
  color: white;
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Glass Effect */
.glass {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
  border-radius: 20px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}

/* Navbar */
nav {
  position: fixed;
  width: 100%;
  top: 0;
  padding: 20px 10%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  z-index: 1000;
}

nav h1 {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 22px;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

nav ul {
  display: flex;
  list-style: none;
  gap: 30px;
}

nav ul li {
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

nav ul li::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  width: 0%;
  height: 2px;
  background: #00f2fe;
  bottom: -5px;
  left: 0;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

nav ul li:hover::after {
  width: 100%;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0 10%;
  text-align: center;
}

.hero-content {
  padding: 50px;
  animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
}

.hero h2 {
  font-size: 48px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.hero span {
  color: #00f2fe;
}

.hero p {
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 18px;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 30px;
  padding: 12px 28px;
  border-radius: 30px;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00f2fe, #4facfe);
  color: black;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: 0.4s;
}

.btn:hover {
  transform: scale(1.1);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00f2fe;
}

/* Section */
section {
  padding: 100px 10%;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Cards */
.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
  gap: 30px;
}

.card {
  padding: 30px;
  transition: 0.4s;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03);
  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.4);
}

.card h3 {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #00f2fe;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 30px;
  font-size: 14px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

/* Animations */
@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* Floating Background Circles */
.circle {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.2);
  animation: float 10s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
}

.circle1 { width: 200px; height: 200px; top: 10%; left: 5%; }
.circle2 { width: 150px; height: 150px; bottom: 15%; right: 10%; }

@keyframes float {
  from { transform: translateY(0); }
  to { transform: translateY(40px); }
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="circle circle1"></div>
<div class="circle circle2"></div>

<nav class="glass">
  <h1>Gurpreet Kaur</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>Home</li>
    <li>About</li>
    <li>Skills</li>
    <li>Contact</li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content glass">
    <h2>Hello, I'm <span>Gurpreet</span></h2>
    <p>
      Senior Agile Project Manager with 10+ years of experience in Cloud, SaaS Platforms, 
      Data Engineering & Dashboard Analytics. Passionate about driving scalable solutions 
      and delivering high-impact technology initiatives.
    </p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Let's Connect</a>
  </div>
</div>

<section id="about">
  <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
  <div class="glass card">
    <p>
      I specialize in Agile/Scrum delivery, Cloud Cost Optimization, Databricks Workspace 
      Management, AWS Infrastructure, and SaaS Dashboard Strategy. 
      I bridge business and engineering teams to ensure smooth execution, 
      measurable impact, and scalable architecture.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="skills">
  <h2 class="section-title">Core Expertise</h2>
  <div class="cards">
    <div class="glass card">
      <h3>Agile & Scrum Leadership</h3>
      <p>End-to-end delivery management for complex enterprise programs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass card">
      <h3>Cloud & AWS</h3>
      <p>Infrastructure planning, cost optimization & performance monitoring.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass card">
      <h3>Data & Analytics</h3>
      <p>SaaS dashboards, cluster metrics, resource tracking & reporting insights.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="glass card">
      <h3>Technical Stack</h3>
      <p>Java, Quarkus, Linux, EC2, System Architecture & DevOps workflows.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <h2 class="section-title">Get In Touch</h2>
  <div class="glass card" style="text-align:center;">
    <p>Open to leadership roles, cloud strategy discussions, and high-impact collaborations.</p>
    <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="btn">Email Me</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  © 2026 Gurpreet Kaur | Designed with Modern Glass UI
</footer>

</body>
</html>
